                                Access Bernie

    Email Bernie about legislative issues of concern to you... Try using
    the form on our email page, or you can use your own email program by
              emailing him a directly at bernie@mail.house.gov.

       Looking for assistance with a problem? Contact our constituent
          advocates directly through out Constituent Services page.

    Also, try stepping on to our Soapbox: sound off to Bernie about this
    month's issue, and your statement could end up read before Congress.


